room_title: Escape room "Who Stole Christmas?" by Unlocked: Escape Room Wooster in Mansfield
room_description: Twas the night before Christmas and all through the house bickering erupted, who knows what about. The family went silent when they heard a car alarm go off outside. They all stepped outside to see what was going on, and the alarm went silent. When they went back into the house they realized all the presents were gone! Who stole them? Will you recover the presents and save Christmas?
